		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="414" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战羊进行拱、角<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">觗</span><span>2段攻击，依次造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">45%,75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战羊开始蓄力，出现冲刺轨迹，4s后冲刺，对玩家造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害，对铁爪造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">暴击</span><span>伤害为30%的必定暴击伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战羊抬起前身，然后迅速扑下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害，若命中铁爪，则造成其当前</span><span color="#ffccbf">12.5%</span><span>生命值的暴击伤害，并令其立即旋转。愤怒状态下，将连续施放3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="442" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当铁爪被战羊的<span color="#ffdfbf">蛮骑突击</span><span>命中2次后，抱头展开</span><span color="#ffdfbf">头鸟坚壁</span><span>，全抗大幅提升，持续30s。若继续被战羊的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">蛮骑突击</span><span>命中，双方将损失20%生命值，并且眩晕8s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战羊抬起前身，然后扑下顺势用角向前顶，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">65%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战羊跑远开始蓄力，准备<span color="#ffdfbf">蛮骑突击</span><span>，4s后冲刺，对玩家造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">300%</span><span>伤害，对铁爪造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">暴击</span><span>伤害为30%的必定暴击伤害，重复5次。命中铁爪的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">头鸟坚壁</span><span>时双方将损失20%生命值，并且眩晕8s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">铁爪从地面衔起一枚谷粒，抛向玩家，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%,20%</span><span>伤害。愤怒状态下，将连续施放3次，每次将抛出3枚谷粒。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">铁爪被战羊的冲刺命中后会撞飞，然后落地膨胀缓冲，随后立即旋转一圈，恢复体型并造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">铁爪被战羊的「跃羊怒遏」命中后会立即开始不断旋转，朝玩家方向行径，触碰持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%,40%</span><span>伤害。若命中战羊，则造成其当前</span><span color="#ffccbf">12.5%</span><span>生命值的暴击伤害并中断技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1183" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">入战后，铁爪和战羊的攻击都会对对方造成伤害；若阵亡一方，则另一方会陷入愤怒，攻击力提升<span color="#ffbfbf">200%</span><span>，且部分技能获得强化。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
